    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661610/extras/dce14d354f410b7ba72dff584ffe7af2.poster.avif?t=1771895202\" width=580 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661610/extras/dce14d354f410b7ba72dff584ffe7af2.webm?t=1771895202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661610/extras/dce14d354f410b7ba72dff584ffe7af2.mp4?t=1771895202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Apopia：糖衣冒险》是一款带有黑暗神秘背景的喜剧冒险游戏。玩家将在游戏中帮助小麦寻找回家的路。在冒险的途中，玩家需要解决谜题并在小游戏中智取各种敌人。同时，玩家还可与动物们对话成为好友或一同面对敌人。一起在这场冒险中，揭开小麦的身世之谜吧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在扮演小麦的过程中您将： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索美丽的幻象世界。了解那些有趣的角色，他们可能只是一只猫，一只鼹鼠，一大群兔子或者其他各种各样的存在。每个角色都拥有独立的个性和背景故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在回家的路上解决各种天马行空的谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人……唔，不过并不是依靠拳头……而是在那些小游戏中智取他们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在节奏游戏中击败黑暗首领。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开小麦的身世真相。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**游戏包含的美术形象可能不适合精神易焦虑人士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661610/extras/a0dfb92704b127d57a8e3b64ff6a7ffc.poster.avif?t=1771895202\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661610/extras/a0dfb92704b127d57a8e3b64ff6a7ffc.webm?t=1771895202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661610/extras/a0dfb92704b127d57a8e3b64ff6a7ffc.mp4?t=1771895202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演奇幻世界中唯一的人类并展开一场奇怪的冒险之旅。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与动物们对话，其中包括一只猫咪……一头变种猫咪。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作 + 解谜 + 音游。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特有的 Boss 战系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70+ 手绘动画。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵感取自 90 年代卡通风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原创配乐。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您甚至可在游戏中领养一只宠物猫咪！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开诸多黑暗之谜，它们将关系到……关系到……到……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VGhlcmUgYXJlIG1vcmUgc2VjcmV0cyB0aGF0IG1vcnRhbHMgY2Fubm90IGtub3cgOik=</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661610/extras/f6b42f6dbc0de39a5a08ef4ca31dc95a.avif?t=1771895202\" width=516 height=288 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动画短片“Apopia：破碎的王冠”公开！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这段动画短片中一睹《Apopia：序章》前发生的种种故事，了解莫利被驱逐出城堡的背后缘由。观看并提升你的试玩体验</p>",
